lyrics:
[verse]
In a world of shadows and unpredictable gloom
I found a flicker of light, a spark in my room
No longer drowning in despair or feeling so coy
I'll paint my heart with colors of happiness and joy

[chorus]
Oh, let's celebrate this vibrant symphony
Break free from the chains, embrace life's ecstasy
A harmonious blend of tears and laughter we employ
We'll sing a melody filled with happiness and joy
